## Design System Rules

### Color Tokens (from design-system.json)

**NEVER HARDCODE COLORS.** Always use theme-aware classes:

**Backgrounds:**
- `bg-background` - Main app background
- `bg-card` - Card/modal backgrounds
- `bg-accent` - Hover/active states
- `bg-primary` - Brand orange

**Text:**
- `text-foreground` - Primary text
- `text-muted-foreground` - Secondary text
- `text-primary` - Brand orange text

**Borders:**
- `border-border` - Default borders
- `border-primary` - Accent borders

